    "Additionally, RL PPO ED and RL A2C ED also outperformed the random algorithm, further emphasizing their superior performance in the evaluated tasks.",
    "In addition, our RL algorithm successfully identified the input leading to the WCET of our sample program, which was developed under the guidance of a domain expert.",
    "ConclusionIn this chapter, we evaluated the performance of GA and RL approaches, specifically A2C and PPO, for estimating the WCET across two case studies: CD and the 6-DOF scenario.We investigated the impact of incorporating diversity as a key component in both the fitness function for GA and the reward structure for RL algorithms.",
    "The results highlighted the critical role of diversity in enhancing the algorithms' ability to explore a broader solution space and identify higher execution times, thus leading to more accurate WCET estimations.",
    "In both the CD and 6-DOF case studies, GA with diversity (GA ED) significantly outperformed GA without diversity (GA E)."
